Text:
Not bagging the uploader or the effort they put in because without them we wouldn't be able to download but the quality of this download is very poor. It's watchable if you are really desperate to see the flick but personally i'd wait for a better copy. I believe ratings are based on 10 being Blu-Ray and 0 being unwatchable and with this in mind i give the following rating;

A/4
V/3

Cheers
